title: Rana Tanveer Hussain wins PP-139 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League (N) candidate, Rana Tanveer Hussain has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-139, Sheikhupura-IV by securing 35,659 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate, Ijaz Hussain who bagged 33,685 votes.
The votersâ€™ turnout remained 49.94%.
